  "bead": {
    "id": "ddx-a06ef04a",
    "title": "graphql: expose needs-human beads and review resolution",
    "description": "PROBLEM\nThe web GUI cannot implement a Needs review filter or submit operator review decisions without GraphQL support. Existing bead queries and mutations expose generic lifecycle operations but not needs-human metadata or explicit review resolution.\n\nROOT CAUSE\ncli/internal/server/graphql/schema.graphql:169-179 defines BeadStatusCounts without needsHuman or workerReady. cli/internal/server/graphql/schema.graphql:2263-2329 defines bead queries but no beadsNeedsHuman query. cli/internal/server/graphql/schema.graphql:3153-3188 defines bead mutations but no beadHumanResolve mutation. cli/internal/server/graphql/resolver_mutation_beads.go:112-156 provides generic beadUpdate but not action-specific resolution with required notes.\n\nPROPOSED FIX\nExtend GraphQL with needs-human fields on Bead, needsHuman/workerReady counts, beadsNeedsHuman query, and beadHumanResolve mutation using action enum retry|split|obsolete|defer, required note, and optional children. Resolvers delegate to bead package helpers shared with CLI.\n\nNON-SCOPE\nFrontend rendering, execute-loop transition changes, or full artifact review chat.\n\nDEPS\nDepends on ddx-c5cab746.",
    "acceptance": "1. schema.graphql exposes Bead.needsHuman, Bead.needsHumanReason, Bead.needsHumanSuggestedAction, Bead.needsHumanSummary, BeadStatusCounts.needsHuman, BeadStatusCounts.workerReady, beadsNeedsHuman, and beadHumanResolve.\n2. TestGraphQLBeadsNeedsHumanQuery verifies needs-human rows include reason/source/suggested action and exclude ordinary open beads.\n3. TestGraphQLBeadHumanResolveRetry verifies retry resolution removes needs_human and appends a resolution event.\n4. TestGraphQLBeadHumanResolveRequiresNote verifies all resolve actions reject empty notes.\n5. TestGraphQLBeadStatusCountsNeedsHuman verifies counts match store.Status().\n6. cd cli \u0026\u0026 go test ./internal/server/graphql/... green.\n7. lefthook run pre-commit passes.",
    "parent": "ddx-ac10e7af",
